sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant NG as Nginx
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant EX as Expense Service
    participant DB as Expense PostgreSQL
    participant K as Kafka
    participant AN as Analytics Service
    participant R as Redis
    participant NO as Notification Service
    participant NDB as Notification PostgreSQL

    User->>FE: Create expense
    FE->>NG: POST /api/expenses
    NG->>GW: Forward request
    GW->>EX: POST /expenses with JWT
    EX->>DB: Save expense
    EX->>K: Publish expense.created
    K->>AN: Consume expense.created
    AN->>R: Invalidate analytics:user:* cache
    K->>NO: Consume expense.created
    NO->>NDB: Create notification
    GW-->>FE: Expense response
    FE->>GW: Refresh dashboard / notifications
